	class='flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 md:flex-row'
>
	<div
		class='[&>p]:mb-4 [&>p>strong]:text-yellow-500 dark:[&>p>strong]:text-yellow-100 [&>p>strong]:font-normal [&>p>strong]:font-mono text-pretty order-2 md:order-1'
	>
		<p>
			I'm a <strong>Full‑stack developer with 3 years of experience</strong>.
			I’ve built production apps with <strong>Angular, React, Next.js, Node (Express/Nest)</strong>
			and care about clean code, performance, and developer experience.
		</p>

		<p>
			I enjoy <strong>solving real problems</strong> and collaborating closely with teams.
			I’m <strong>proactive, communicative, and focused on outcomes</strong>—shipping features,
			improving codebases, and measuring impact.
		</p>

		<p>
